lead_paragraph: Chelsea captain John Terry expects Jose Mourinho to be a success at Manchester United, saying the Portuguese is the right manager to lead the 13-time Premier League champions back into contention for major honors.

headline.print_headline: Terry Backs Mourinho to Succeed at Manchester United
